snippet.textDisplay:
All the beats are quite similar in this season. With same boring start for most of the song. I listen to Tu Hi Tu, Bholay Bhalay Saiyan and Baliye all the time but even I can't differentiate them and now this. This same start of every song has to stop. 
 No singer/Music director no matter how much talented can never give 10 hits simultaneously. 
Though you people are giving chance to Shuja Haider, Faakhir, Shiraz and Jaffer Zaidi others but everything other song by Noori is unacceptable. They ruined Haroon's song for many people by adding unnecessary rock, folk fusion crap which ended up being perceived "loud noise" by many people. Par Chanaa and Saiyaan were awesome but you can't expect same people to give you ten hits one after another. 
You should try different music directors and composers for every song. Max 2 song for each.  No more than that.
Love Strings production though. Don't let then go.
